HEADWORD: Offskip
<hw>Off"skip`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Off</ets> +
<ets>-skip</ets>, as in <ets>landskip</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Paint.)</fld>
